sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as Test Caller
    participant Executor as BridgeToolExecutor
    participant Catalog as CompiledBridgeToolCatalog
    participant Policy as IToolExecutionPolicy
    participant Approval as IToolExecutionApprovalService
    participant Tool as GatedHandoffPreviewTool
    participant Audit as IAuditSink
    participant Log as RecordingBridgeLogger

    Caller->>Executor: ExecuteAsync bridge.gatedHandoffPreview requestId=request-123 operationId=operation-456
    Executor->>Log: Bridge tool execution started
    Executor->>Log: Redacted request payload
    Executor->>Catalog: TryGetTool bridge.gatedHandoffPreview
    Catalog-->>Executor: Descriptor and compiled tool instance
    Executor->>Log: Manifest and capability metadata
    Executor->>Policy: EvaluateAsync ToolExecutionSecurityContext
    Policy-->>Executor: Allow
    Executor->>Approval: Not invoked because ApprovalRequirement=NotRequired
    Executor->>Tool: ExecuteAsync explicit scoped handoff request
    Tool->>Tool: Preserve or generate request and operation ids
    Tool->>Tool: Validate objective, repo path, and validation requirements
    Tool->>Tool: Redact secret-shaped input
    Tool->>Tool: Emit risk flags for deployment, destructive git, secrets, Codex, commands, and mutation scope
    Tool->>Tool: Build scoped task text, validation checklist, stop conditions, approval reminder, and redaction notice
    Tool-->>Executor: BridgeToolResult previewOnly=true with no side effects
    Executor->>Log: Bridge tool execution completed
    Executor->>Log: Redacted result payload
    Executor->>Audit: RecordAsync CodexHandoffPreview envelope
    Executor-->>Caller: Structured gated handoff preview
